		<hr size="1">Okay, so I was bored in LOIO one night and was amusing a friend with stupid enchanter tricks.  The best part was when I did Illusion Tree, but for some reason could still move around, and I had sow!  </P><P>Then I dropped a batwing on the ground, cast minor illusion, and picked up the batwing.  We waited.  A troll comes along...tries to pick up the bag...after a couple of tries he says "The bag cons yellow to me!"</P><P>Anyone come up with some really unusual ways to have a good time?</P><P></P><P>Kiana, <BR>Countess of Morcrayr<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
