		<hr size="1">  I like to spend time either at the newbie/pod lift in kelethin or orc hill in Kelethin. When there are a bunch of newbies around I will often charm an orc and have it attack something (usually another orc) and then run away to see how long it takes for one of the newbies to say "what the hell". I usually tell them it's all over a girl or say something to the affect of geez take it on springer. <BR>  Another is when I am just standing there talking to someone I do random illusions. If they turn away for any reason I quickly cast minor illusion and they think I disappeared. <BR>  Neither of these is particuraly exciting but since I am only lvl 14 the running around newbie areas with illusion werewolf idea won't be happening for awhile. ;(</P><P>Laenyeni<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
