		<hr size="1">Two favourites from the Felwithe area are Illusion:Skeleton and Minor Illusion, near the guards, with SoW and Levitate.<BR>As a Skeleton, I run around casting. (It gets interrupted of course, but you just cannot beat that laughter!)  You always get someone who tries casting on you, even though your name pops up when they target you.  When you start casting back, even though they're buffs, you can nearly see the fear in their eyes.<BR>I like to cast Levitate on them, makes 'em panick a bit, the new ones anyway. ;o)</P><P>With Minor Illusion near the guards, I always come out as on of the fire pots that are there.  With Lev on, you rather look like a UFO careening through GFAY toward Crushbone. Ahh.</P><P>Fiergus Starcaster<BR>Guild Leader {Peep Cartouche}<BR>Druzzil Ro</P><P>u can also drink the mana, if ure group needs you, or you are oom and your charm spell has worn off -Xarse<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
